ConfigurationOption.Value: select i.LBL_IMAGESID, i.DESCRIPTION, i.HASLD, i.ORGID, i.SITEID, i.ENTITY_NAME, i.ENTITY_IMAGE, i.CHANGEBY, i.CHANGEDATE, i.REFID from lbl_images i

List.ListEntry: i.refid in ( select wonum from workorder where ( wonum in ( select lbl.refwo from lbl_labtrans lbl where lbl.lbl_transtype = 'PLAN' and lbl.laborcode = '${MX_LABOR_CODE}' ) ) and status in ( select value from synonymdomain where domainid = 'WOSTATUS' and maxvalue in ('APPR','INPRG') ) )
